            "param_text": "<ul><li><strong>Motor</strong>52V 4160W Mid Drive Motor</li><li><strong>Battery</strong>52V 26Ah Lithium Battery(1352Wh)</li><li><strong>Charger</strong>58.8V 5A Charger</li><li><strong>Charger Voltage</strong>100-220V, 50-60Hz</li><li><strong>Controller</strong>52V 80A Smart Controller</li><li><strong>Display</strong>LED Display</li><li><strong>Light</strong>Front White Headlight</li><li><strong>Bluetooth</strong>Bluetooth Speaker(Optional)</li></ul>"
